God knows.

21:02.727 --> 21:04.395
He wants every gun-pit
on a party line

21:04.429 --> 21:06.731
So we got a man
listening at all times.

21:16.975 --> 21:18.675
<i>Hey, you want some limit stakes</i>

21:18.710 --> 21:20.210
<i>In there, sergeant?</i>

21:20.245 --> 21:23.046
Yeah, go get it.

21:48.432 --> 21:49.867
The japs are on the move.

21:49.901 --> 21:51.768
Hoosier and runner,
I want you to set up an lp.

21:51.803 --> 21:54.370
<i>- 30 yards inside the tree line.
- Aye aye, captain.</i>

21:54.404 --> 21:56.304
<i>I want your mg smack
up on the wire,</i>

21:56.339 --> 21:58.339
But preset placements
so you can move back.

21:58.373 --> 22:00.206
How thin are we on the line, sir?

22:00.241 --> 22:01.776
We're putting the
cooks on the line,

22:01.810 --> 22:03.815
But don't have enough cooks.

22:03.849 --> 22:06.585
Best case, we hear the shit going
off on the other side of the ridge.

22:06.619 --> 22:10.089
