to go around us to hit the airfield.

22:10.123 --> 22:12.491
We're too spread out,
same as puller and the 7th.

22:12.525 --> 22:15.427
Well, same old story
for the 1st marines.

22:15.461 --> 22:18.896
Two-hour watches tonight
all along the line.

22:20.166 --> 22:21.835
What you guys smokin'? Raleighs?

22:21.869 --> 22:24.171
That's our allotment.

22:24.206 --> 22:27.174
Only the officers get
the lucky strikes.

22:27.208 --> 22:30.477
Well, I can't have
my platoon suffering.

22:32.312 --> 22:35.548
Eyes open, ears up.

22:35.582 --> 22:37.283
Aye aye, sir.

22:37.317 --> 22:39.385
That was a gesture of a gentleman.

22:39.419 --> 22:42.588
<i>- Hoosier: We must really be fucked.
- Runner: Yep.</i>

22:50.763 --> 22:53.264
Thanks, evans.

22:57.869 --> 23:01.037
Here, sergeant,
while it's still dry.

23:01.938 --> 23:03.739
Thanks.

