A buddy of mine's up
there with the 5th,

23:09.911 --> 23:12.779
Played the trumpet with
me in the division band.

23:13.881 --> 23:17.183
You any good on the trumpet?

23:17.217 --> 23:21.253
Nah, mostly because
I play the trombone.

23:27.728 --> 23:29.829
That was a joke.

23:29.864 --> 23:31.798
Look at you.

23:31.833 --> 23:33.634
We'll make a marine out of you yet.

23:33.668 --> 23:35.836
<i>It's starting to come faster.</i>

23:35.870 --> 23:39.473
<i> </i>

23:39.508 --> 23:43.110
Sir, it's briggs at the outpost.

23:44.112 --> 23:45.345
Puller. Report, over.

23:45.379 --> 23:48.414
I got the whole fucking jap army

23:48.448 --> 23:50.849
Headed your way,ver.

23:54.052 --> 23:57.419
When they're past you,
pull out and hook up with able company.

23:57.453 --> 24:00.855
<i>1st battalion, hold your fire
as long as possible.</i>

