- Man: Aye aye, sir.</i>

24:15.569 --> 24:16.969
- Rodriguez.
- Sir.

24:17.004 --> 24:19.939
Run as much ammo down there
as you can. - Aye aye, sir.

24:26.712 --> 24:28.912
They're not just coming
across the matanikau.

24:29.947 --> 24:31.614
They're coming right at us.

25:01.573 --> 25:03.840
<i>Squad leaders,
give me a head count!</i>

25:03.875 --> 25:07.243
<i>- Man #2: First squad's up.
- Man #3: Second squad's up.</i>

25:07.277 --> 25:09.945
- Everyone okay?
- Yes, sergeant.

25:13.215 --> 25:15.049
<i>Japs!</i>

25:16.885 --> 25:19.252
Japs left, crawling in!

25:27.559 --> 25:28.893
On your right!

25:31.966 --> 25:34.232
