- Man: Changing the box.</i>

25:35.568 --> 25:37.736
Cover.

25:47.050 --> 25:49.084
Reload.

25:58.933 --> 26:02.603
<i>- Man: Medic!
- Man #2: Reload.</i>

26:13.215 --> 26:17.319
<i>- Man: Cease fire!
- Man #2: Cease fire!</i>

26:19.989 --> 26:21.824
<i>Contact on the left.</i>

26:21.858 --> 26:23.459
<i>No shit.</i>

26:23.493 --> 26:26.128
that's jp for you.

26:26.163 --> 26:27.863
- How much ammo you got?
- Half a belt.

26:27.898 --> 26:29.565
- That's it?
- Yeah.

26:29.600 --> 26:31.534
