26:31.568 --> 26:34.704
fuck!

26:41.612 --> 26:43.180
Fuck!

26:50.255 --> 26:52.423
Read!

26:59.631 --> 27:01.466
Fuck, my gun's jammed!

27:04.803 --> 27:07.005
<i>Evans, mend the gun.</i>

27:11.878 --> 27:14.312
<i>Grenades out there!</i>

27:18.485 --> 27:19.886
You're up!

27:26.594 --> 27:28.695
Sergeant!

27:29.897 --> 27:31.965
Sergeant, they broke through!

27:31.999 --> 27:33.900
They overran us. Both guns are out.

27:33.934 --> 27:36.169
<i>Conserve your ammo.
We're running low.</i>

27:36.203 --> 27:37.704
Evans, we're going.

27:37.738 --> 27:40.473
We gotta help jp.

27:40.507 --> 27:42.876
Where the hell is my glove?

27:42.910 --> 27:47.047
- Lapointe, the tripod.
- Aye aye, sergeant.

27:48.550 --> 27:51.719
ahh.

27:51.754 --> 27:54.089
Cover cover!

27:54.124 --> 27:56.225
<i>To my right! To my right!</i>

27:56.260 --> 27:59.628
Get it on there.

27:59.663 --> 28:02.297
<i>Fill in that gap!</i>

29:11.927 --> 29:13.527
Let's go!

29:24.440 --> 29:27.541
<i>Ammo ammo!</i>

29:28.910 --> 29:30.777
Reload!

29:30.811 --> 29:33.146
<i> </i>

29:43.589 --> 29:45.322
- How many got through?
- At least 50.

29:45.357 --> 29:47.657
- Ahh!  Shit!
- You okay?

29:47.692 --> 29:49.659
- Yeah, I'm fine. I'm fine.
- Here they come!

29:52.962 --> 29:54.596
Jesus christ.

30:16.380 --> 30:18.047
God damn!

30:47.438 --> 30:50.573
<i>I need a head and ammo count.</i>

30:50.607 --> 30:53.942
<i>Man #2: First squad: Two down,</i>

30:53.976 --> 30:55.677
<i>80 rounds remaining.</i>

30:55.711 --> 30:59.613
