Jp, cover me. - John, wait.
What are you doing?

31:03.184 --> 31:05.285
John, what are you doing?

31:19.598 --> 31:21.332
John, move, left flank.

31:21.366 --> 31:23.467
John, get outta there!

31:25.036 --> 31:26.303
Grenade!

31:31.409 --> 31:34.411
- What the hell was that?
- Now you've got a clear field of fire.

31:34.446 --> 31:36.847
- A clear field--
- lapointe, evans,

31:36.882 --> 31:39.183
Stay here, hold this position.

31:40.853 --> 31:43.654
- I'm gonna get more ammo.
- Morgan: Hurry back.

31:51.997 --> 31:53.931
Ammo for the 30s!

31:53.965 --> 31:55.566
Come on, come on, come on!

31:55.600 --> 31:57.535
That's all we got.

32:03.641 --> 32:06.644
- Ahh!
- Ahh!

32:21.394 --> 32:23.762
Ugh!

32:52.257 --> 32:56.026
